 that</a>, which is why he briefly pretended he was going to take Tesla pri=
vate. There is probably some truth to some of these complaints.=C2=A0But th=
ere is maybe no better counterexample in the history of capitalism=C2=A0<em=
>than Tesla</em>. Elon Musk had a dream of making electric cars cool and ub=
